ific manner  and without policy recommendations  among public policymakers  business professionals  and the academic community  Contact a librarian Accacia Mullen Email Me Contact  5th floor  Preston Library  540  464 7250 Social  Facebook Page Subjects  Chinese  Economics   Business   EC BU  English Rhetoric Humanistic Studies   ERH  French  History  International Studies  IS  Library Research  Psychology  Spanish Next  Databases   Last Updated  Mar 11  2016 9 49 AM URL  http libguides vmi edu EC435 Print Page Login to LibApps Report a problem  Subjects  Economics   Business   EC BU Tags  bu  ec  economics  institutions 